~ Primitive [in-built] Data Types: 

i. integral = int,char.
ii.bool = True/False.
iii.float = float, double.

~ ASCII Codes are given: 
Number is used to represent a Character. eg. A-65, B-66,.... Z-90, a-97, b-98.... z-122. 

~ Modifiers: 

i. Unsigned: [for int and char] 
ii. Long: [used for printing long num's]